---
title: Veggie Burrito Bowls with Beyond Meat® and DIY salsa
description: Get ready for burrito vibes but minus the mess! Hearty sweet potatoes and Beyond Meat® on a bed of pepper-onion rice make for a satisfying supper. This bowl is made even better by two tasty toppers: lime cream and DIY salsa!
